title: Video: Recapping the Seattle Seahawks’ win over the San Francisco 49ers
text:
Seattle Times columnist Larry Stone and writer Bob Condotta recap the Seattle Seahawks’ win over the 49ers Thursday night.
 
Bob Condotta : 206-515-5699 or bcondotta@seattletimes.com ; on Twitter: @bcondotta . Bob Condotta covers the Seahawks for the Seattle Times. He provides daily coverage of the team throughout the year.
